      "id": "step-7-full-picture",
      "title": "The Full Picture",
      "description": "Here's ZeroLeaks at a glance. The scanner flows from the CLI or programmatic API through the Scan Engine, which coordinates the multi-agent team (Strategist, Attacker, Evaluator, Mutator, Inspector, Orchestrator) against a Target LLM. Agents draw from the Probe Library (15+ attack categories) and the Knowledge Base (CVE techniques, payloads, exfiltration vectors, defense bypasses) to systematically test system prompt security. Results are scored from 'secure' to 'critical' with detailed findings, defense profiles, and actionable recommendations.",
